snippet.title: Ravenswatch | Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Ravenswatch Early Access on Steam now: http://nacon.me/Ravenswatch

The wait is almost over! 
After an incredible year of early access, we're thrilled to announce the official release date of Ravenswatch is set up for September 26th on PC! 

Prepare for an unforgettable journey as the realms of dark fantasy come to life and face off against the ultimate challenge: Baba Yaga herself.

Now's the time to rally your friends, sharpen your skills, and prepare for the ultimate showdown! 

Ravenswatch will be available the September 26th on PC and Fall 2024 on PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S. 

-------------------------------
